Copy the files to the other instances.
----------------------------------------
$ scp -r . pradeeban@146.193.41.145:/home/pradeeban
or just,
$ scp gsd-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar pradeeban@146.193.41.145:/home/pradeeban
and
$ scp -r conf pradeeban@146.193.41.145:/home/pradeeban/


